{"tid":2162624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人hea住毒遊奧地利","createTime":"2020-08-18T08:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:01:54.000Z","uid":136778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a46f68023f9fe50319485176549e91f86cb211","tid":2162624,"uid":136778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"第一次寫遊記  1999希望唔會睇得好辛苦<br />\n睇番facebook原來差唔多隔左成年無去旅行<br />\n8月27~9月7 去左11日左右   淨係去左奧地利<br />\n去之前成日比人問點解唔去埋捷克 , 匈牙利<br />\n因為我個人去旅行比較hea 唔想咁趕 <br />\n係香港生活節奏已經好快<br />\n唔想連唯一出國放鬆既時間都要咁趕咁chur<br />\n講番個行程先<br />\n<br />\n8月27   HK&gt;Doha<br />\n8月28   Doha&gt;Vienna<br />\n8月29   Vienna<br />\n8月30   Vienna&gt;Salzburg<br />\n8月31   Salzburg&gt;Hallsatt&gt;Obertraun<br />\n9月1     Obertraun&gt;Gosausee&gt;Salzburg<br />\n9月2     Salzburg&gt;Innsbruck<br />\n9月3     Innsbruck&gt;K&ouml;nigssee<br />\n9月4     K&ouml;nigssee&gt;Golling&gt;Salzburg<br />\n9月5     Salzburg&gt;Vienna<br />\n9月6     Vienna&gt;Doha<br />\n9月7     HK<br />\n<br />\n不停來來回回Salzburg 可能你會話ON9 <br />\n但就係唔想咁趕  留耐少少睇多D唔同野<br />\n放住幾張相先 希望唔好爛尾<br />\n相多數都係IPHONE X 影<br />\n影得太唔好插得太大力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTeGBbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTeGBbd.jpg&h=1b6bea2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvfnkCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvfnkCX.jpg&h=626e783d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2crebKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2crebKF.jpg&h=23ea25bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7csMNh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7csMNh5.jpg&h=cc71a266&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b6ed19cf5e5da45c21d2dd8c9ecc1b2a6d1138c","tid":2162624,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5911d6c7a4b019de66f51580c27aeddda8